## Desktop Application Features

### Feature 1: Local CSV File Loading
- File picker dialog
- Support for 3 CSV formats (Task Definitions, Intake Events, Duration Manifest)
- Drag-and-drop CSV files onto window
- Recent files list in File menu

### Feature 2: Real-time Convergence Visualization
- Progress bar showing Round 1, 2, 3...
- Count of tasks adjusted each round
- Estimated time to completion
- Cancel button if calculation takes too long

### Feature 3: Sequence Timeline Tab
- Grouped by business domain (PAYROLL, SETTLEMENT, etc.)
- Horizontal scrollable Gantt chart
- Task bars colored by validity (green/red)
- Deadline lines drawn at intake times
- Right-click context menu for task details

### Feature 4: Violation Highlighting
- Table view of deadline misses
- Filter/sort by severity
- Export to CSV or print

### Feature 5: Settings & User Preferences
- Theme (Light/Dark mode)
- CSV file directory (remember last location)
- Display density (compact/comfortable/spacious)
- Timezone override (for daily schedule calculations)

### Feature 6: Help & Documentation
- In-app help panel
- View documentation files
- About dialog

