## Technology Stack Summary Table

| Layer | Technology | Version | Purpose |
|-------|-----------|---------|---------|
| **Backend: Distributed Computation** | Orleans | 8.x | Grain-based parallel execution |
| **Backend: Desktop Orchestration** | Aspire / .NET Hosting | 8.x | Orleans silo embedded in desktop app |
| **Frontend: Desktop GUI** | WinUI 3 | 1.5.x | Native Windows 11 UI |
| **Frontend: UI Framework** | MVVM Toolkit | 8.x | ViewModel binding & commands |
| **Frontend: Data Grid** | WinUI DataGrid | 8.x | Task list & violations table |
| **Frontend: Charts** | Win2D / Canvas | 1.x | Custom Gantt chart rendering |
| **Frontend: Dialogs** | WinUI Dialog Control | 1.5.x | File pickers, error dialogs |
| **Data Format** | CSV (CsvHelper) | 31.x | CSV file parsing |

