## Web GUI Component Architecture

### Page 1: Dashboard

**Layout**:
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Dashboard                                           │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [← Back] [Refresh] [Export]                        │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                     │
│ Execution Overview                                  │
│ ┌──────────────┬──────────────┬──────────────┐    │
│ │ Total Tasks  │ Valid        │ Invalid      │    │
│ │ 150          │ 145 (96%)    │ 5 (4%)       │    │
│ └──────────────┴──────────────┴──────────────┘    │
│                                                     │
│ Convergence Progress                                │
│ ├─ Round 1: 127 tasks changed position (+15 delta) │
│ ├─ Round 2: 18 tasks changed position (+3 delta)   │
│ ├─ Round 3: 0 tasks changed (CONVERGED)            │
│ └─ Total Time: 1.24 seconds                        │
│                                                     │
│ Critical Path: 06:00 → 17:30 (11.5 hours)         │
│                                                     │
│ Deadline Misses: 5                                  │
│ ├─ Task 42: Completes 14:15, deadline 14:00      │
│ ├─ Task 87: Completes 11:45, deadline 11:30      │
│ └─ [Show All]                                      │
│                                                     │
│ Business Groupings (click to drill-down)           │
│ ├─ PAYROLL (95 tasks) → 06:00–14:00, 0 misses    │
│ ├─ SETTLEMENT (40 tasks) → 09:00–15:30, 2 misses │
│ └─ REPORTING (15 tasks) → 17:00–18:00, 3 misses  │
│                                                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Page 2: Groups (Sequence Visualization)

**Layout**:
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Group: PAYROLL                                      │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [← Back] [Download Timeline] [Export to ICS]       │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Stats: 95 tasks, 93 valid, 2 invalid              │
│ Critical Path: 06:00 → 14:00 (8 hours)            │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                     │
│ TIMELINE GANTT CHART (horizontal scrollable)       │
│ ├─ 06:00  07:00  08:00  09:00  10:00  11:00 ...   │
│ │                                                  │
│ ├─ Task 1  [████─── Extract ]                     │
│ ├─ Task 2  |      [─── Validate ]                 │
│ ├─ Task 3  |           [██ Transform]             │
│ ├─ Task 4  [XXXX─ Invalid:deadline]               │
│ ├─ Task 5  |           |   [─ Load]               │
│ ├─ Task 6  |           |      [─ Publish]         │
│ │...                                              │
│ └─ Task 95|..................    [Cleanup]         │
│                                                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Task Details (click task to expand)                │
│ Task 4: INVALID                                    │
│  Precursors: Task 1, Task 2                        │
│  Scheduled Start: 10:30                            │
│  Calculated Start: 10:45 (due to Task 2 delay)    │
│  Duration: 120 min (est.)                          │
│  Planned End: 12:45                                │
│  ⚠️ Deadline: 12:00 → MISSES by 45 minutes         │
│  Reason: Task 2 completed too late                │
│                                                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

